.
├── config
└── hostap
    ├── src
    ├── hostapd
    └── wpa_supplicant

1. Unmodified source code in hostap dir, which clone from git://w1.fi/srv/git/hostap.git.
2. Use marvell custom config files:
       cp config/hostapd-marvell.config hostap/hostapd/.config
       cp config/wpa_supplicant-marvell.config hostap/wpa_supplicant/.config
